<section id="shippingZone">
  <title>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>shipping zones</primary>
      <secondary>creating new</secondary>
    </indexterm>Shipping Zone</title>
  <para>To create a new Shipping Zone, select the NEW button.
  The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para>
<screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/shippingZone.png"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Create New Shipping Zone</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
</para>
  <para>When creating a new Shipping Zone, you are presented
  with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Name</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the name of the Shipping Zone.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a description to identify the Shipping Zone.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
